  <h1 class="title">How To Upload</h1>
  <h2 class="category">If your exam have individual documents / pictures</h2>
  <p>
    <ul>
      <li><span class="icon-chevron-right"></span>Zip compress all those files.</li>
      <li><span class="icon-chevron-right"></span>Name it as "division-yourname.zip".(change 'division' to the division you applied to, change 'yourname' to your firstname-lastname)</li>
      <li><span class="icon-chevron-right"></span>Hover over the options on the upper left of the screen and click Submit.</li>
      <li><span class="icon-chevron-right"></span>Browse your zip file and click ok.</li>
      <li><span class="icon-chevron-right"></span>You will see a confirmation if you have successfully uploaded the file.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>
